# Cloudflare Pages redirects.
# The engine binaries are too large for CF Pages (25 MiB/file limit), so they
# live as GitHub Release assets. /releases/latest/download/ always resolves to
# the newest release, so new game builds need a new release — NOT an edit here.
#
# NOTE: a cross-origin (CF Pages -> github.com) fetch of wasm/pck only works if
# GitHub serves the asset with permissive CORS. If a browser test shows the pck
# blocked by CORS, replace these with a same-origin Cloudflare Worker proxy
# (see README "If CORS blocks the binaries").

/index.wasm   https://github.com/ConsssLabs/play/releases/latest/download/index.wasm   302
/index.pck    https://github.com/ConsssLabs/play/releases/latest/download/index.pck    302
